{"id": 1269, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在吃早餐这件事情上有什么习惯？", "description": "我是今天煎饼果子来一套明天桃园眷村来一套的随机播放模式。", "record_count": 4052, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161010145229pOUyGbPtKTMdAZc1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-14T03:00:34Z", "options": [{"id": 123904, "content": "好想早点起床吃顿大餐结果....", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794828}, {"id": 125184, "content": "想起什么是什么，而且想吃吃不到会抓狂而死", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89309}, {"id": 123905, "content": "喝豆浆的话必须配油条...", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794832}, {"id": 124417, "content": "双荷包蛋的面条", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796315}, {"id": 125185, "content": "冬天必须喝热的！热豆浆热咖啡热燕麦粥实在不行也必须喝杯热水，不理解外国人365天天天喝凉的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798497}, {"id": 123906, "content": "必须撸一发 喝点营养快线", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192232}, {"id": 124162, "content": "油条必须要有豆浆", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593560}, {"id": 124418, "content": "什么都吃，except翔", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796361}, {"id": 124930, "content": "一定要香", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628335}, {"id": 123907, "content": "早上要有鸡蛋??", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790639}, {"id": 124163, "content": "学生党一定要有鸡蛋牛奶！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795527}, {"id": 124419, "content": "喝豆浆配油条真是个真爱的routine啊??", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756627}, {"id": 123908, "content": "早起。慢做。享受生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541033}, {"id": 124164, "content": "第一口必须是甜的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751856}, {"id": 124420, "content": "反正不喝牛奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715687}, {"id": 312581, "content": "有人为我准备就好，吃啥无所谓", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364552}, {"id": 312582, "content": "偶尔会顺便帮同事带两份早餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364552}, {"id": 123910, "content": "不能凉，不要太油腻～", "image": null, "praise_count": 179, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788336}, {"id": 124422, "content": "围绕着蛋展开", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733262}, {"id": 125190, "content": "点一杯摩卡 外加一份鲜奶面包 所以 我胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798521}, {"id": 123911, "content": "最好能控制在一分钟内解决的", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793331}, {"id": 124167, "content": "3块钱包子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789051}, {"id": 125191, "content": "一定会冲一碗红豆薏米粉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796860}, {"id": 134152, "content": "蒸鸡蛋煮鸡蛋，再来一个西红柿?一根黄瓜，或者包子稀饭，胡辣汤什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834713}, {"id": 123912, "content": "麵包,麥片加奶粉,腸粉,饅頭,油條,餛飩,雞蛋,牛奶....有時混搭有時單吃,但必須吃飽?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 468910}, {"id": 124168, "content": "面包 牛奶 脆脆之类的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795529}, {"id": 124169, "content": "不吃辣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795539}, {"id": 124425, "content": "做份早餐 得早起半小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796376}, {"id": 124937, "content": "一定要美味，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797594}, {"id": 123914, "content": "反正不想吃面包，太没味道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794851}, {"id": 124170, "content": "十年沒吃過早餐了⋯⋯算習慣嗎⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111455}, {"id": 124426, "content": "可以不吃饭，必须喝咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709067}, {"id": 125450, "content": "一定要有暖胃的热饮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779447}, {"id": 123915, "content": "热的，要搭配合理，营养均衡", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787286}, {"id": 124427, "content": "热的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792768}, {"id": 124172, "content": "通常和午餐一起吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795543}, {"id": 124428, "content": "一定要自己做", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782251}, {"id": 124684, "content": "必须有牛奶", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791187}, {"id": 124940, "content": "主要看我几点起床，起的早就找间早餐店慢慢吃，起的晚有什么吃就吃什么～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797144}, {"id": 123917, "content": "法国的早餐都是甜的，吃了很多年，习惯了，一回国吃咸的还有点不习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793524}, {"id": 124173, "content": "一定要有熱的，喝的，一定要有煮雞蛋，一定要有菜和饃饃，一定要有水果。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795546}, {"id": 124429, "content": "燕麦牛奶枸杞黑芝麻鸡蛋，缺一不可…已吃5年，完美肌肤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791618}, {"id": 124174, "content": "喜欢在吃饭的时候听英语 虽然不怎么听懂哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795545}, {"id": 124430, "content": "一定要有热的！！不管是豆浆还是粥还是甜豆腐脑！只有冷冷的牛奶的早饭根本不算什么早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750634}, {"id": 126990, "content": "饭可以不吃，必须有冷藏新鲜牛奶.", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 774940}, {"id": 128270, "content": "要吃带汤类的东西，绝不吃干巴巴的面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704221}, {"id": 124175, "content": "不吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417222}, {"id": 124943, "content": "一定要陪着手机吃?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533368}, {"id": 125455, "content": "简单 还是复杂 完全看心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800314}, {"id": 124176, "content": "喜欢吃面条...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790192}]}